[32m│[0m - **Backend**: Likely Ruby/Sinatra (based on response patterns)              [32m│[0m
[32m│[0m - **Content Type**: `text/html;charset=utf-8`                                [32m│[0m
[32m│[0m                                                                              [32m│[0m
